article_title: US president previously said he was 'outraged' by aid worker strike.
sentence: We're  still  waiting  for  a  readout  of  the  call  that's  taken  place  between  Joe  Biden  and  Benjamin  Netanyahu  -  until  then,  here  are  five  things  the  US  president  said  earlier  this  week  about  the  Israeli  strike  that  killed  seven  aid  workers  in  Gaza:  Biden  said  he  was  "outraged  and  heartbroken"  at  Israel's  killing  of  the  World  Central  Kitchen  employees.
